results.name: Continued fraction for Gamma(1/3).
link: Harry J. Smith, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..1000
Index entries for continued fractions for constants
formula: Note that 3 * Gamma(1/3) * Gamma(2/3) = 2 * Pi * sqrt(3).
program: (PARI) { default(realprecision, 1080); x=contfrac(gamma(1/3)); for (n=1, 1000, write("b030651.txt", n, " ", x[n])); } \\ _Harry J. Smith_, Apr 20 2009
